data.description: PRICED TO SELL!!Must See.  This charming  well maintained 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath. Plenty of room for the family.  Homeowners will love the private , downstairs master suite with its separate garden tub , step in shower and large walk in closet. The bright and open kitchen features plenty of beautiful  cabinets, Gibraltar counters as well as the BRAND NEW  energy efficient Stainless Steel Appliances.Home is energy efficient as well. Open concept. Brand  New Carpet and Paint. 3 bedrooms, full bath and media room located upstairs. Fully fenced back yard and front yard  landscaping . In additional, the beautiful gated community of Sterling Lakes offers a variety of outdoor amenities , including a full -size covered basketball court, tennis court, playgrounds, pool and more! Only minutes to Downtown Houston, Houston Medical Center, Galleria Area, Pearland Town Center, Shopping, Dining, Dow, LNG ,BASF in Freeport, Chevron and Phillips 66 in Old Ocean.
